      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 48,
      "start": 449.296,
      "end": 466.164,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "return"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "常见意思是回来，但在这课里，它的意思是退回、归还。你可以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return a book"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把书还回图书馆；也可以"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "return a product"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，把商品退回商店。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 49,
      "start": 466.514,
      "end": 477.178,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "return"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "课文里那个人问："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Can I return these two tickets?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "意思是“我可以退掉这两张票吗？”这两张票被退回来了，但日期不对。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 50,
      "start": 477.527,
      "end": 480.207,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
