      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三个词："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pity"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 51,
      "start": 480.557,
      "end": 482.093,
      "speaker": "B",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pity"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 52,
      "start": 482.443,
      "end": 492.507,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "pity"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在这里表示令人失望、可惜的事。计划失败了，票卖完了，你可以说："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "What a pity!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 53,
      "start": 492.857,
      "end": 504.457,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "vocab",
      "scene_meta": {
        "word": "pity"
      },
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Susan"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "说这句话的时候，不是大哭，也不是生气，而是很失望：他们已经赶到剧院了，可是票已经"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 54,
      "start": 504.806,
      "end": 518.526,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "grammar"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "不是背一整张情态动词表，而是看"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "could"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "在买票现场分别完成什么任务。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 55,
      "start": 518.876,
      "end": 535.683,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第一组是猜测："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The play may begin at any moment."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may begin"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“可能马上开始”。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "It may have begun already."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may have begun"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "表示“可能已经开始了”。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 56,
      "start": 536.033,
      "end": 553.252,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第二组是礼貌请求："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I have two tickets please?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "和"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I have those two tickets please?"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "都是在请对方把票卖给我。"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "比直接说"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Can I have"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "更软一点。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 57,
      "start": 553.602,
      "end": 565.366,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "第三组是无奈选择："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "I might as well have them."
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "这里"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might as well"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "的意思是：不是最理想，但既然这样，我也只好要了。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 58,
      "start": 565.716,
      "end": 581.507,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以这样记：故事开头的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "may"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是担心和猜测；售票窗口的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "May I"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "、"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "Could I"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是礼貌买票；结尾的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "might as well"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "是失望后的接受。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 59,
      "start": 581.857,
      "end": 591.009,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "grammar",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "语法跟着情绪走："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "worry, polite asking, sudden hope, wrong date, sad acceptance"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "。这比单独背规则更容易记住。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 60,
      "start": 591.359,
      "end": 613.022,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "好，把今天的"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out story"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "放进你自己的生活。想象你要买电影票、演唱会票、展览票，或者预约一个活动名额。你看到"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "sold out"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，然后有人"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "returned two tickets"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "，你很快去抢，却发现日期或场次不对。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 61,
      "start": 613.372,
      "end": 628.308,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "可以用这个小框架："
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "The tickets were sold out. Then someone returned two tickets. I hurried to buy them, but they were for next Wednesday's performance. I might as well wait or choose another day."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "i": 62,
      "start": 628.658,
      "end": 638.874,
      "speaker": "A",
      "scene": "you_too",
      "scene_meta": {},
      "segments": [
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "下面练习里，用"
        },
        {
          "lang": "en",
          "text": "word bank"
        },
        {
          "lang": "zh",
          "text": "填三个空，把“票卖完了、有人退票、结果场次不对”说清楚。"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
